Belan, B. D., O. Yu. Luk'yanov, M. K. Mikushev, I. N. Plokhikh, and N. A. Stepkin.
1992.
An automated archive of observational data obtained with an airborne sounding of the atmosphere.
Atmos.
Ocean Optics 5(10):1081-1087.
A computer-assisted archive structure and content that was created on the basis of the aircraft atmospheric-sounding results and that contains atmospheric aerosol concentration and chemical and gas composition data in different regions is described.
A list of cities is given for which the data are available.
