Proc.
Inst.
Exp. Meteorol.
35(113):52-66.
An analytical solution of a simplified aerosol transport equation in the lower stratosphere has been completed.
The equation allows us to describe the significant evolution stage of stratospheric aerosol layers.
Simple formulae for aerosol bulk concentration fields and total particle numbers on the various heights are obtained.
