1989.
Aerosols.
Moscow.
Nauka.
142p.
This book, intended for a broad range of readers, is devoted to the quickly developing field of aerosol studies.
The knowledge of aerosol properties, their formation, and behavioral laws is necessary for pure air, water, and soil conservation (industry emissions due to technology backwardness amount to 99% of extracted raw material mass).
